1 → 2 → 3 → 4

Change 1 is a single sort — do it first and verify it does not affect chokidar events before moving on. Change 2 is the highest impact change — test it on a large PDF (100+ pages) before proceeding. Changes 3 and 4 carry the lowest risk and go last.